                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2021-09-22/debates/8516a540-019d-4e9f-82a1-bcf9b2dc5e87/HigherEducation(FreedomOfSpeech)Bill(TwelfthSitting)"><u>Twelfth Sitting: Col. 359-398</u></a></p>
                </td>
